data.name: MessageBoxButtons
desc: defines constants for the possible message box button combinations.

items.name: BUTTONS_OK_CANCEL
lines: specifies a message box with \"OK\" and \"CANCEL\" button.

items.name: BUTTONS_YES_NO
lines: specifies a message box with \"YES\" and \"NO\" button.

items.name: BUTTONS_YES_NO_CANCEL
lines: specifies a message box with \"YES\", \"NO\" and \"CANCEL\" button.

items.name: BUTTONS_RETRY_CANCEL
lines: specifies a message box with \"RETRY\" and \"CANCEL\" button.

items.name: BUTTONS_ABORT_IGNORE_RETRY
lines: specifies a message box with \"ABORT\", \"IGNORE\" and \"RETRY\" button.

items.name: DEFAULT_BUTTON_OK
lines: specifies that OK is the default button.

items.name: DEFAULT_BUTTON_CANCEL
lines: specifies that CANCEL is the default button.

items.name: DEFAULT_BUTTON_RETRY
lines: specifies that RETRY is the default button.

items.name: DEFAULT_BUTTON_YES
lines: specifies that YES is the default button.

items.name: DEFAULT_BUTTON_NO
lines: specifies that NO is the default button.

items.name: DEFAULT_BUTTON_IGNORE
lines: specifies that IGNORE is the default button.
